<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Man I have no clue what you were doing wrong, but I have a 32 troll warrior on Tarew Marr.  I open with this like everyone here mentions.  Occasionally I hit for low end damage (around 60) but usually I smack em good for 110+ per hit.  <BR>
<BR>
Also someone mentioned that even if you switch weapons you have to wait based on the Weighted Axe's delay...uh uh...nope..incorrect.  <BR>
<BR>
I smack em good then switch out to my Mith 2h.  I almost immediately follow up with another hit.  Granted the Mith 2h haste takes the delay down to at most 33.  At this point people may start arguing over the haste % of the Mith.  All I know is that I swing faster with my Mith 2h than with a Runed Falchion (Delay 34.)  BTW Assuming that the delay is no better than 33 on a Mith 2h that takes the damage delay ratio to 13.03 damage per second...neat thing about that is that the damage is still based off the base delay of 40 (Greater damage for 40+ weapons)<BR>
<BR>
Hmmmm got off topic...<BR>
K in summary...set up some inventory buttons...set up some Melee 1 & 2 buttons...WHACK em good with the Weighted...switch...carve em up with something else.</font></td></tr></table>
